PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1992-2722 which reappointed Dr. HARRY C. EASTMAN of Toronto, Ontario, to be Chairman of the Patented Medicine Prices Review Board, by revoking the words "for a term of two years" and substituting therefor the words "FOR A TERM ENDING MARCH 7, 1995".
